title: The Credit Cleanup Book: Improving Your Credit Score,
description:
The Credit Cleanup Book: Improving Your Credit Score, Your Greatest Financial Asset by Shindy Chen

Requirements: ePUB reader, 1.6 MB

Overview: Many consumers don't understand the basics of credit reporting and scoring or how this information is used by lenders and service providers today. This book was written to remedy that. The no-nonsense guide teaches readers about credit reporting and scoring, shows them how to obtain and read their credit reports and scores, and outlines ways to remove negative and inaccurate items. Readers will also learn about the latest consumer protection legislation concerning credit and lending, as well as about changes in lending practices that can impact their financial lives
